Jomolith_Play_Player_Camera_State_CameraLogic_CameraState --> Jomolith_Play_Player_Camera_State_CameraLogic_CameraState : ZoomedOut
Jomolith_Play_Player_Camera_State_CameraLogic_CameraState_FirstPerson --> Jomolith_Play_Player_Camera_State_CameraLogic_CameraState_ShiftLockFirstPerson : ToggleShiftLock
Jomolith_Play_Player_Camera_State_CameraLogic_CameraState_FirstPerson --> Jomolith_Play_Player_Camera_State_CameraLogic_CameraState_Unlocked : FirstPersonExited
Jomolith_Play_Player_Camera_State_CameraLogic_CameraState_ShiftLock --> Jomolith_Play_Player_Camera_State_CameraLogic_CameraState_ShiftLockFirstPerson : FirstPersonEntered
