Jomolith_Play_Player_Camera_State_CameraLogic_CameraState_ShiftLockFirstPerson : OnFirstPersonExited → FirstPersonExited
Jomolith_Play_Player_Camera_State_CameraLogic_CameraState_ShiftLockFirstPerson : OnToggleShiftLock → ShiftLockExited
